                     <interp inst="t17780218-38-off207" type="offenceSubcategory" value="wounding"></interp>
               wilfully, maliciously, and feloniously shooting at 
                     
                        <persName id="t17780218-38-victim477" type="victimName">
                           Henrietta
                            Knightley
                        <interp inst="t17780218-38-victim477" type="surname" value="Knightley"></interp>
