                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780218-38-off207 t17780218-38-victim477"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , with a certain pistol, loaded with gunpowder and a leaden bullet, on the <rs id="t17780218-38-cd208" type="crimeDate">18th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780218-38-off207 t17780218-38-cd208"></join>, the said Henrietta being in the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t17780218-38-person478">
                        James
                         Draper
                     <interp inst="t17780218-38-person478" type="surname" value="Draper"></interp>
